Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.23,0:22:47.35,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(120,0)}Wake up fail again attempt to whisper back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.35,0:22:50.41,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(0,200)}Do you have the same dream every night
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.41,0:22:56.42,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(0,200)}震えてた瞬間へ繋がる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.42,0:22:59.75,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5}そうさ 君も全てを賭けて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.75,0:23:02.90,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(0,200)}戦う場所へ飛び出したら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.90,0:23:04.12,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5}You can believe it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.12,0:23:08.95,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(0,200)}That's the way it have to be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.95,0:23:11.98,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5}Win or not what's worth the meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.98,0:23:15.23,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(0,200)}Nowhere so deep fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.23,0:23:22.87,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(0,200)}見失ったものが多い気がした
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.87,0:23:24.43,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,0)}Blink about the miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.43,0:23:26.16,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,0)}So ask yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.16,0:23:27.60,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5}Walk 響く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.60,0:23:30.60,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5}あの日のリズム今に刻む
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.60,0:23:32.34,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(120,0)}Yes reaching out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.34,0:23:36.90,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(0,200)}Walk 遠くに見てた未来掴んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.90,0:23:40.01,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5}Red pulse rushing through and I can hear you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.01,0:23:43.10,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(0,200)}溢れたノイズをかき鳴らす
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.10,0:23:48.56,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(0,200)}未来図は泡のように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.56,0:23:52.39,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(0,200)}浮かんで 弾け飛んだ
